{{#> base subject="Your Settlement Statement — {{txnId}}"}}
  {{#*inline "body"}}
    <h2>Settlement Statement</h2>
    <p>Dear <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>,</p>
    <p>Your gold transaction has been settled. Please find your settlement summary below. A detailed PDF statement is attached to this email for your records.</p>

    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="label">Transaction Reference</div>
      <div class="value" style="font-size:14px;font-family:monospace;">{{txnId}}</div>
      <div class="label" style="margin-top:12px;">Net Remittance (USD)</div>
      <div class="value">{{netRemittanceUsd}}</div>
    </div>

    <p>The net remittance amount has been (or will be) transferred to your registered bank account. Please refer to the attached PDF for a full breakdown of gross proceeds, costs, fees, and net payable.</p>

    <p>If you have any questions about your settlement, please contact your assigned agent or our finance team.</p>

    <hr class="divider" />
    <p style="color:#888;font-size:13px;">Please retain this statement and the attached PDF for your financial records and tax purposes.</p>
  {{/inline}}
{{/base}}
